txt.en: Lost spirits can be found along the river Gladden.\n\nYou should defeat lost spirits.
You have defeated many lost spirits along the river Gladden, making the Vales of Anduin safer.
A strange darkness has come to the Vales of Anduin. Lost spirits move along the river Gladden. These fell beings should be defeated if the Vales are to remain safe.
Lost spirits move along the river Gladden.
